<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.214758>
    dc:description "FIGURE 4 21. Male antennal club (4 6), pronotum (7 9), metaventral process (10 12, in lateral view), apical portion of pro tibia (13 15), protrochanter and profemur (16 18), and mesotrochanter and mesofemur (19 21) of Pselaphodes spp. 4, 7, 10, 13, 16, 19. P. daoyaoensis. 5, 8, 11, 14, 17, 20. P. hui. 6, 9, 12, 15, 18, 21. P. maoershanus. Scales: a f, m r = 0.3 mm; g i = 0.2 mm; j l = 0.05 mm." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/214758/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

